long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copy for UIKit streamlines your workflow by automatically converting copied Figma variable values into the corresponding UIKit values. When you copy a color, text style or other design variable in Figma, the extension instantly replaces it with the appropriate UIKit value and updates your clipboard, making your design-to-code process seamless and efficient.
